{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2027239f4c","title":"给李达的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ed7faff8d9","index":0,"year":1954,"month":12,"day":28,"articleId":"2027239f4c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"3f10183ca3","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"2027239f4c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李达，号鸽鸣，当时任武汉大学校长。"},{"id":"a759ac4654","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"2027239f4c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指李达写的《胡适的政治思想批判》和《胡适思想批判》。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3eb78ec521","type":"title","text":"给李达\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"2027239f4c"},{"id":"3f10183ca3","type":"paragraph","text":"鹤鸣兄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"2027239f4c"},{"id":"a759ac4654","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月二十日的信及两篇文章，收到看过了，觉得很好。特别是政治思想一篇，对读者帮助更大。似乎有些错字，例如“实用主义者主张物质的第一性和意识的第二性”。此外，在批判实用主义时，对实用主义所说的实用和效果，和我们所说的大体同样的名词，还需加以比较说明，因为一般人对这些还是混不清的。宇宙“是一篇未完的草稿··几句话，也须作明确的批判。你的文章通俗易懂，这是很好的。在再写文章时，建议对一些哲学的基本概念，利用适当的场合，加以说明，使一般干部都能够看懂。要利用这个机会，使成百方的不懂哲学的党内外干部懂得一点马克思主义的哲学。未知以为如何","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"2027239f4c"},{"id":"75d1bdc38f","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"2027239f4c"},{"id":"86ac3d2dfb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"2027239f4c"},{"id":"6402040bba","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年十二月廿八日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"2027239f4c"}],"page":{"id":"55f6f644f6","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"2027239f4c","start":395,"end":395}}}},"__N_SSG":true}